org.anchoranalysis.plugin.mpp.segment.bean.optimization.mode

Class TransformationAssignMode<S,T,U>

  • Object
    • AnchorBean<AssignMode<S,T,U>>
      • AssignMode<S,T,U>
        • TransformationAssignMode<S,T,U>

  • public class TransformationAssignMode<S,T,U>
extends AssignMode<S,T,U>
    Applies a transformation to the kernel-type U to calculate the Energy used as the primary readout during optimization

    However, the kernel manipulation layer will always function in terms of the untransformed Energy (U) as the optimization continues

    The final transformation, as well as what's "reported" out use the TRANSFORMED (S) version

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
